The data source is the official game client and there is no access to other test data.

Even if the price is displayed in gold- ONLY SUPERTESTERS IN THE SPECIAL CLIENT OF THE GAME CAN BUY THIS !!!

Package.Name: Horizontal Compact Techtree
Package.Description: This mod simply shortens the arrows in the horizontal tree of studies, so as not to scroll the left-right research sheet, plus maximally compactly disposes tanks in the tree of investigation in width.
